data.description: Great 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath, 2 car Garage with an Open Floor Plan and Tile throughout. Features include Granite Counters, Breakfast Bar, Stainless Steel Appliances, New Roof 2019, 18'x7' Screened Porch, and Huge 38'x14' Screened Patio. Conveniently located behind the Merritt Square Mall, Publix, Restaurants, Shops, and quick ride over the causeway to the beach.
